        public <T> T build(java.lang.Object initializationObject,

        Builds an Object with the given type and initializes it from the given Object parameter.
        Type Parameters:
        T - is the Type of the reference which the returned Object is given to
        Parameters:
        initializationObject - is the initial value of the Object
        context - an EserialContext containing information about the context of the element to be built
